The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for estimating the position and orientation of surgical instruments from X-ray images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and control (cs.RO), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper uses deep learning methods, which suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category.
